title: ISic001768. I.Sicily inscription 001768
body:
Facsimile Images

[Ου]αλεντῖνος
ἐτῶν ο´
πατὴρ τέκνων
δέκ(α)´ ((⳨))

Apparatus criticus

Text of Orsi; alternatively [Β]αλεντῖνος
3: The rho apparently has the form of a crossed Latin D; Strazzulla suggested πατὴ(ρ) δὲ

English translation

Valentinos, 70 years old, father of ten children ((staurogram))

commentary

bibliography

  • Orsi 1893 285 no.30 https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715
  • Strazzulla 1897 140 no. 169 https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001390
